videos.description: North Carolina freshman Coby White creates separation with a step back for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: White drills step-back 3 for UNC

videos.description: Duke junior Marques Bolden has to be helped off the court after going down with a left leg injury.
videos.headline: Bolden helped off court after hard fall
